        `,technologies:["ASP.NET","MS-SQL","AJAX","JavaScript","HTML","CSS","Bootstrap"],learnings:"Enhanced full-stack development skills, gained experience in enterprise architecture, and improved team collaboration abilities."},{id:4,title:"Power Platform Solutions - SunTrust Banks",type:"Company Project",company:"Infosys Ltd",client:"SunTrust Banks",briefDescription:"Developed Power Platform solutions including Power Pages and Power Apps for SunTrust Banks, focusing on interactive web experiences and efficient business solutions.",detailedDescription:`
